1.1 /2020-05-01
Adds
1.Tabs: Add mouse wheel event to scroll tabs.
Fixed
1.Grid: Fixed the issue that hidden columns are still visible when fixed(left/right).
2.Grid: Fixed the issue that check_on_click was not working.
3.Popup: Fixed the issue that the parent popup widget would also be closed when clicking outside of the child popup widget to close.

1.0 /2020-01-01
Adds
1.Adds z.form.Form, a form manager that allows you to easily manage the form.
2.Validator: Adds alphanumeric_dash rule to verify the alphanumeric underline and dash value.
Fixed
1.Pagination: Fixed paging information is not updated when setting total.

0.6 /2019-11-01
Adds
1.Adds fade/slide/zoom animations.
2.Grid: Adds row striped background color.
3.Modal: Adds optional sizes.
4.Pagination: Adds the 'layout' property to set the layout and child element visibility.
Fixed
1.Popup(Tooltip/Popover/Modal/MessageBox): Fixed an issue where element is lost due to continuous pop-up when the content is an element in dom.
2.Grid/TreeGrid: Fixed an issue when scrolling to make the selected data visible, the scrollbar is not syncing.


0.5 /2019-10-01
Adds
1.Grid: Compare function can be added to the column for custom sorting.
2.Popup(Tooltip/Popover/Modal/MessageBox): Adds default animation effects.
3.Notification: Adds type (success/info/warning/error) to display different notification types.


0.4	/2019-09-01
Adds
1.Adds z.form.Validator to validate form fields.

0.3	/2019-08-01
Adds
1.Adds z.widget.alert() method to display an alert box with a specified message and an OK button.
  Adds z.widget.confirm() method to display a dialog box with the specified message, along with an OK and a Cancel button.
  Adds z.widget.prompt() method to display a dialog box that prompts the visitor for input.
2.Grid:Columns can be minimized。
Fixed
1.Tooltip: Fixed open/close exception caused by delay.
2.Menu: When the mouse slides out,the expanded menu item is not collapsed,

0.2	/2019-07-01
Adds
1.Adds z.widget.tooltip() method to add tooltip (open/close) event listener 
  Adds z.widget.tooltip.init() method to initialize all tooltip components (data-toggle="zw-tooltip") 
  Adds z.widget.tooltip.open(hostEle, tooltip) method to open a tooltip on hostEle 
2.Adds z.widget.popover() method to add popover (open/close) event listener 
  Adds z.widget.popover.init() method to initialize all popover components (data-toggle="zw-popover") 
  Adds z.widget.popover.open(hostEle, content) method to open a popover on hostEle 
3.Adds z.widget.modal(modalContentEle, props/false) method to toggle modal open/close. If the second argument is false, close the modal, otherwise open modal 
  Adds z.widget.modal.init() method to initialize all modal components (data-toggle="zw-modal") 
  Adds z.widget.modal.on() method to add modal (open/close) event listener 
4.Popover/Tooltip will close when the window loses focus (blur)。
Fixed
1.Grid/TreeGrid: when deleting/adding data items, the header check column status is not updated.
2.Notification: wrong position when position is "bottom_left" and direction is "right"

0.1	/2019-06-01
Release.